    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 13 article, which referred incorrectly to three neighbors of Leonard and Harriet Walit</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A front-page article on Thursday about community spirit on the Brooklyn block that was the scene of a fatal explosion referred incorrectly to three neighbors of Leonard and Harriet Walit, the couple who died. A baby whom the Walits had helped move into a car was with Melanie Morton, not with a couple from the block. And the couple's names are Andreas Killen and Marie Sacco, not Andreas and Maria Sassos.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
